commit_message: Refactoring, use of clap and cue.
Implement dependency as a mixture model using the 2nd rule of multiplication.
Added a test case for path priors. Still failing right now.
Removed path_prior. Reimplemented dependencies. TODO implement proper prior het distribution such that expectation for zero read depth equals given heterozygosity.
Improved numerical stability, moved functions into Rust-Bio.
Record and use complete depth information.
Fixed bug in log prob sum.
Cap max and min prior for dependencies.
Use log prob add instead of log prob sum.
Finished FPR vs TPR plot. TODO: show behavior of FDR controlled calls over depth.
Allow more characters in sample names.
Use less samtools procs for preprocessing.
Adapted to rust-htslib API changes and tried to format BCF output properly. This still fails due to segfaults.
Better solution, but fails due to incompatibility between htslib and rust pipes.
Calculate maximum likelihood genotype and control FDR.
Parentheses for grammar. Remove ambiguity from grammar.
Added parser for queries using rust-peg.
Added preprocessing via samtools and bcftools.
Initial import for the first snippets.
